            , were indicted for <rs id="t18170219-129-off725" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170219-129-off725" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170219-129-off725" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18170219-129-cd726" type="crimeDate">8th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170219-129-off725 t18170219-129-cd726"></join>, two jackets, value 3s.; 3lbs of soap, value 1s.; 5lbs of sugar, value 2s.; three knives, value 1s.; and two forks, value 6d.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18170219-129-victim995" type="victimName">
                     Philip 
                     Barnes
                  <interp inst="t18170219-129-victim995" type="surname" value="Barnes"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170219-129-victim995" type="given" value="Philip"></interp>
